high_descs: Turn to your right move slightly then face to right top shelf
Pick up the credit card beside the vase
Turn to your right then walk straight turn left facing the center table
Put the credit card on the left plate on the center table
Pick up the plate with credit card
Turn to your left walk few steps then turn right walk towards the shelf
Put the plate with credit card on the lower right side of the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with credit card on the lower shelf

high_descs: Turn around to face shelf with vase.
Pick up credit card from shelf, right of the vase.
Turn right then left and proceed to coffee table.
Place credit card on left side plate at bottom of table top.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
Turn left and proceed to shelf.
Place plate with credit card on the shelf, on the right hand side, on the right of the empty box.
anns.task_desc: Move credit card and plate to a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and look at the shelf behind you
Pick up the credit card from the shelf
Turn back around and then turn to the left and walk toward the table
Put the credit card on the plate on the left
Pick up the plate on the left
Turn around and then turn toward the right and walk to the shelf near the box
Put the plate down on the shelf to the right of the box
anns.task_desc: Get the credit card on a plate and next to the box

high_descs: Turn around and step left to face the black shelf.
Take the credit card off the shelf.
Turn around and walk forward, hanging left to the short side of coffee table.
Place the credit card on the white plate on the left.
Pick up the plate.
Turn left and walk back to where the black shelf is.
Put the plate with the credit card on it on the right side of the bench under the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on it on a bench.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the shelf above the bench.
Pick up the credit card from the shelf.
Turn around and walk over to the table in the middle of the floor.
Put the credit card on the plate on the left side of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Walk back over the bench under the shelf.
Put the plate on the right side of the bench.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a credit card on it on the bench.

high_descs: Turn right and then walk to the wall then turn right again to face the shelf hanging on the wall.
Pick up the credit card to the right of the vase.
Turn around and walk until you are even with the glass coffee table to your left and then turn to the left and walk forward so you are in front of the coffee table facing it.
Put the credit card on top of the square white plate sitting to the left of another plate just like it.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on top of it.
Go back to where you were at the end of step 1.
Place the plate with the credit card to the right of the box that is on the lower shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a credit card on it on the shelf.
